{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5d13e45d6c","title":"中央文革调查组接见首都红代会在宁战士时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"d829eee377","index":0,"year":1967,"month":8,"day":21,"articleId":"5d13e45d6c","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"大联合","id":"18bf6a78fe","type":"主题"},{"name":"暴力和武斗","id":"3bff1d2fc6","type":"主题"},{"name":"张春桥","id":"471a503675","type":"人物"},{"name":"中央文革调查组","id":"942c59ecdc","type":"人物"},{"name":"关键人物文稿","id":"c20d333791","type":"文稿大类"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"},{"name":"发言","id":"e23dcf99fa","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"中央文革","id":"ef71f03227","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenku","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第一版）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":"","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"65f109e920","name":"中央文革调查组"}]},"publication_details":{"wenku":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"43e89cdcda","type":"title","text":"中央文革调查组接见首都红代会在宁战士时的讲话","index":0,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"c89ba8a1bf","type":"paragraph","text":"八月廿一日下午，中央文革江苏调查组接见了首都红代会大专院校在宁战士。总理秘书宋皋同志讲话要点如下：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"742b391e44","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）南京文化大革命开展比较早，交大，南大都比较早，但形势较复杂；","index":2,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2e0f440843","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）要研究解决五月十四日后南京争论的焦点是什么，要历史的唯物的研究；","index":3,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"e711879b31","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）五月十四日张春桥同志讲话是中央肯定的；","index":4,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"0be874e60b","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）如果都是造反派，为什么会出现这样的局面，有没有前台？有没有后台？有没有后台的黑后台？","index":5,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"8ad5213b5f","type":"paragraph","text":"（五）你们要宣传毛泽东思想，制止武斗，建立革命新秩序。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"78723ade48","type":"paragraph","text":"（首都大专院校红代会华东联络站《华东通讯》第十期）","index":7,"publicationId":"wenku","articleId":"5d13e45d6c","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}